    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "I am writing with the regard to the interview we discussed last week. Unfortunately, I might not be able to come at the time we agreed upon. I received a job interview last night, and I set an appointment with the recruiter at the time that overlaps with our interview.",
        "That appointment is very important to me, so I am afraid that I might not be able to show up at the time that we agreed upon. Therefore, I was wondering if we can nicely move our interview to the other day, or later in the same day at your convenience. I sincerely apologize for the changes and any inconvenience that I may cause.",
        "I also have some questions regarding the content of this interview. I would be grateful if you can tell me the length of the interview and if there is any test included. I believe your answers will help me be better prepared for the interview day.",
        "Thank you in advance for your understanding and support!",
        "Sincerely,",
        "Catherine Tian"
    ],
